To use the application you need to:

Go to "https://newsapi.org" to register for a key.
Copy the key to ".env.example" file "NEWS_API_KEY" variable.

Go to "http://api.weatherapi.com" to register for a key.
Copy the key to ".env.example" file "WEATHER_API_KEY" variable.

The "WEBPAGE_BG_IMG_SRC" variable is not mandatory.
This variable will set the background of the page to an image of your choosing.
To use this variable you need find a link for an image anywhere and copy the link to the variable.

After that you need to rename the ".env.example" to ".env".